# source_path|dest_path|mode|level|reason
home/neople/game/Script.pvf|rootfs/home/template/init/Script.pvf|0644|required|神迹玩法主体，直接覆盖清风默认 PVF
home/neople/game/df_game_r|rootfs/home/template/init/df_game_r|0755|required|神迹 df_game_r，作为默认覆盖版本参与镜像打包
home/neople/game/libfd.so|rootfs/home/template/neople/game/libfd.so|0755|required|神迹 run 脚本实际预加载的 C++ 注入库
home/neople/game/channel_info/channel_info.etc|rootfs/home/template/neople/game/channel_info/channel_info.etc|0644|required|神迹游戏侧频道信息，与清风默认版本不同
home/neople/game/channel_info/version|rootfs/home/template/neople/game/channel_info/version|0644|required|神迹游戏侧频道信息版本号
home/neople/channel/channel_amd64|rootfs/home/template/neople/channel/channel_amd64|0755|required|神迹 run 实际启动的频道进程
home/neople/channel/channel_info/channel_info.etc|rootfs/home/template/neople/channel/channel_info/channel_info.etc|0644|required|神迹频道侧 channel_amd64 依赖的频道信息
home/neople/channel/channel_info/version|rootfs/home/template/neople/channel/channel_info/version|0644|required|神迹频道侧频道信息版本号
dp2/|rootfs/home/template/init/dp.tgz|0755|required|神迹 VMDK 内完整 dp2 目录会整体重打包为 dp.tgz
dp2/libdp2pre.so|rootfs/home/template/init/dp.tgz|0755|required|若源目录缺少 libhook.so，则复制 libdp2pre.so 为 libhook.so 以兼容当前 Docker 启动链路
